The body of a form two student was on Thursday morning found near their home in Kajulu, Kisumu county.It is believed that the St Dominic Burkina Secondary School student was murdered by her boyfriend on Wednesday night.Police have arrested the 22-year-old suspect for questioning."The suspect, a farmer, had a relationship with her," said county commissioner Mohamed Maalim.Maalim said a panga and blood-stained clothes were found in his house.The body was taken to Jaramogi Oginga Odinga Teaching and Referral Hospital mortuary.Read: Girl &lsquo;hacked into pieces by brother&rsquo; over Weetabix buried in KiambuAlso read: JKUAT student killed in Ruiru hostel fire